summary: A home that belonged to a Dark elf thief named Murloc
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/svt3s8.jpg[/IMG]

A home that belonged to a Dark elf thief named Murloc.
Located in the Windhelm slums.

If and when asked to overwrite select \\\\\\\"yes to all\\\\\\\" its just the resources I have used
and wont damage your game. This also ***REQUIRES*** Dragonborn DLC***
